* [[Henri Maspero]]: La Composition et la date du Tsu tchouan. Melanges chinois et boudhiques, Volume 1, 1932, pp. 139-215
* [[Chauncey S. Goodrich]]: A Note on the Textual Criticism of the Formula for the Bow-and-Arrow Gifts in the Tso chuan. JAOS, Volume 78, No. 1 , 1958), pp. 41-49
* [[Ronald Egan]]: Narratives in Tso Chuan. HJAS, Volume 37, No. 2, 1977, pp. 323-352

